text: The Battle of Worcester was the final battle of the English Civil War. Oliver Cromwell and the Parliamentarians defeated the Royalist, mainly Scottish, forces of King Charles II on September 3, 1651 at Worcester, England. The 16,000 Royalist forces were defeated by the 28,000 strong "New Model Army" of Cromwell. == Other websites == *Battleground pictures * Worcestershire CC: Historic Environment and Archaeology Service: The Battle of Worcester *http://www.british-civil-wars.co.uk/military/1651-worcester.htm *http://www.clangarra.com/battle%20-%20worcester.htm Worcester Category:Worcester Category:1651 Category:17th century in England Category:1650s in Europe Worcester
